OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine, some fair weather
OL,7,Fcloud will bubble up in the afternoon.
OL,8,FGentle winds and becoming very warm.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry, settled and warm
OL,11,Fevening and largely sunny. Remaining
OL,12,Fdry for the rest of the night with
OL,13,Fclear spells, but perhaps more cloud
OL,14,Fspreading in from the west later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FSome early morning patchy
OL,17,Fcloud clearing to leave a dry day with
OL,18,Fplenty of sunshine. However eastern
OL,19,Fareas may see more in the way of cloud
OL,20,Finto the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
