OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry with very warm sunshine on
OL,7,FWednesday and Thursday. Cloudier later
OL,8,FThursday into Friday with the risk of
OL,9,Fa few showers.
